{"tid":38693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁粉肉麻高叫「好特首」","createTime":"2016-12-14T05:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T10:24:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4036748ea78f43a11ba6eb970ace4a3b032067b","tid":38693,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:56:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161214/19865031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161214%2F19865031&d=2O%2FuI0XC9AMasLbiUOLmrGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=8065d31f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161214%2F19865031&h=969e88ec\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161214/19865031</a><br />\n<br />\n梁粉肉麻高叫「好特首」<br />\n<br />\n11,863<br />\n ■大批梁粉昨日在特首辦外高叫挺梁口號，引來其他請願人士不滿。<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n■大批梁粉昨日在特首辦外高叫挺梁口號，引來其他請願人士不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】早前突然宣佈不連任特首的梁振英，昨日獲20多名「珍惜群組」和「保衛香港運動」的「梁粉」到場「贈興」，但他們不斷高叫挺梁口號，引來其他請願人士非常不滿。<br />\n團體轟：停一停得唔得<br />\n梁振英在特首辦內回應傳媒提問後，就現身特首辦示威區，20多名保衛香港和珍惜群組成員即高喊「梁振英！好特首！」、「梁振英，感激你！」口號，其間梁面露滿足笑容，一邊擺出手勢示意有關人士停止叫喊。不過他們未有聽從梁要求，繼續高喊口號，梁振英在有關人士叫喊近一分鐘後，再舉手示意對方停止，聆聽其他示威者訴求。<br />\n20多名保衛香港和珍惜群組成員做法，終引來其他請願者不滿，有請願人士斥：「你哋停一停得唔得呀？」梁即再示意有關人士停喊口號，並與多名保衛香港運動成員握手，包括人稱「收工男」的保衛香港運動召集人傅振中。傅邊與梁握手邊說：「支持你。」並送上有成員簽名的紀念卡。新聞統專員馮煒光其後更在個人facebook上載有關照片，指梁示意粉絲停止叫喊的手勢「好cute」，又稱「有記者說：劉德華也好興咁！」<br />\n■記者林俊謙  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n預算案應已訂具體內容<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n新民黨今料批准葉劉參選"},{"pid":"b3c103677cb12e443b6a12e369b93bf997dbdb17","tid":38693,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:56:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161214/large/14la3p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161214%2Flarge%2F14la3p10.jpg&h=5eab0071&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95037ae181c7f1055f8f1fe0d833d090015abd99","tid":38693,"uid":57157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:57:25.000Z","msg":"我淨係見到一大堆岩岩失業嘅人"},{"pid":"a00efaa97e0873dcc5eedcf1fcdefc9f9becea83","tid":38693,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:58:01.000Z","msg":"起多D樓"},{"pid":"2c86ef4ad13e7cd2c97a6f76ad6c3ff1a4ac2b68","tid":38693,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:59:25.000Z","msg":"如果得20個人叫好<br />\n咁係咪姐係其他人覺得佢唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b88406564409de0995617e3fa5c40b50fc013a","tid":38693,"uid":11643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T06:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我淨係見到一大堆岩岩失業嘅人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我淨係見到一大堆垃圾"},{"pid":"45a0540ac68fdf7414a62919b80ebb0eed6dc660","tid":38693,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T06:32:59.000Z","msg":"所以我支持689連任多3屆"},{"pid":"17df702b1e9cf8772103afa59c7e7675730176ed","tid":38693,"uid":38552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:17:39.000Z","msg":"我比較想知，如果689下台後，下屈仲會唔會請呢班打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d09cc0cc134d87e2d4ac8c82fd3665591d52c89","tid":38693,"uid":7080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"創造就業機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af44b3ea1f6d43e1100b5b30904e65994e988399","tid":38693,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:29:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa8a71acd81c735b7034f09e2537ddf18a3195da","tid":38693,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:30:57.000Z","msg":"點解會講得出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccc0d65b188dca75bea57689a6de361da6db66a","tid":38693,"uid":52651,"like":0,"disl